        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">SATELLITE EVENTS TO PRIMA 2017 OAXACA, MEXICO</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <h4>CALL FOR PROPOSALS FOR SATELLITE EVENTS TO PRIMA 2017 OAXACA, MEXICO<br><small>
                    August 14-18 2017</small></h4>

                    <p>PRIMA2017 is on its way, the organization is going smoothly and preparations are already under way to have an excellent experience in Oaxaca in August 2017. As in similar events, this is a great opportunity to gather specialists from all over the world.</p>
                    <p>The Organizing Committee calls for applications for financial assistance to organize a satellite conference to PRIMA2017, this may be on close dates before or after the event in Oaxaca and may be anywhere in México. Please submit a proposal explaining the title and areas to be covered by the conference, a brief exposition of the importance of the área and a list of tentative invited speakers and expected number of participants. The proposal must include: title of the conference, organizers and a contact organizar. The proposals must be sent to:
                    <strong>Dr. Daniel Juan</strong> <em>daniel<i class="fa fa-at" aria-hidden="true"></i>matmor.unam.mx</em>, and <strong>Dr. Jose Seade</strong> <em>jseade<i class="fa fa-at" aria-hidden="true"></i>im.unam.mx</em>.<br><br>
                    Deadline for submissions: January 31st 2017.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

